Here is how to setup the unilang system.

How do we view the output of any agent?  For debugging purposes.  Tail agent logs, redirect standard input and output.
How to do this without becoming root? make alternative directory for these things
How do we restart agents without manually doing all those things.  /etc/init.d/agent restart
How do we have them automatically deregister once they are terminated? code in unilang


